suite.doc: This file is filled with tests, and is linked to the steps file via Gherkin methodology. Cannot mix BDD and DDT(data-driven-test), that's why there is no scenario outline. Test setup is used for prerequired steps and starting the browser. Test Teardown closes the browser and takes a screenshot if the test fails.
